Comment: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:00.52,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,烦躁地堵上耳朵\N
Comment: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:07.74,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,	究竟为了什么互相伤害?
Comment: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.57,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,	Can you hear my heartbeat
Comment: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:15.12,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby I trust you my friend
Comment: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:19.08,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,被绝望侵袭的心的角落\N
Comment: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:22.79,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,重叠交错 矛盾的影子\N
